# cereal-box

## Description
cereal-box is a serialization library that exposes defined functions through a custom Django template tag and a JSON API.

## Example
	# models.py
	import django.db.models
	class Example(django.db.models.Model):
		text = django.db.models.CharField(max_length=20)


	import cereal_box
	cereal_box.register(Example, [cereal_box.functions.filter()])

...

	import cereal_box
	cereal_box.call('example', 'filter')
